2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the problem of sampling and reconstruction of a continuous-time signal, which is a common topic in information theory. 
3. cs.OH (Other Computer Science) - The paper discusses a specific application of optical time-of-flight imaging sensors, which could be considered an "other" topic in computer science. 
4. cs.SP (Signal Processing) - The paper discusses the problem of signal reconstruction, which is a common topic in signal processing.
